make you feel like he's the only one for you.

298
00:23:00.050 --> 00:23:02.720
Oh, gosh, how embarrassing!

299
00:23:03.380 --> 00:23:07.020
Uh, you know, uh, um...

300
00:23:07.020 --> 00:23:08.860
